<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and manage personal information on our simple web page. We are committed to respecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices regarding your data.
</p>

<p>
    1. Information Collection:

    We collect limited personal information from visitors on our simple web page. The information we collect may include:

    Cookies and Usage Data: We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to collect information about your interactions with our website and to improve your user experience.

    Contact Information: If you voluntarily provide us with your contact information (such as name and email address) through a contact form or any other means, we will store this data for communication purposes only.
</p>

<p>

    2. Information Use:

    We use the collected information for the following purposes:

    To improve user experience: We may analyze user behavior and website interactions to enhance the functionality and content of our simple web page.

    To respond to inquiries: If you contact us through the provided contact information, we will use that information to respond to your questions or requests.

    To personalize content: We may use cookies and usage data to tailor the content and advertisements you see on our website.
</p>
<p>
    3. Data Sharing:

    We will not share your personal information with third parties unless:

    You have given explicit consent for us to do so.
    It is necessary to comply with legal obligations or to protect our rights and the safety of others.
</p>
<p>
    4. Data Security:

    We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, please note that no data transmission over the internet can be guaranteed to be entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee the security of the information you transmit to us.
</p>
<p>
    5. Third-Party Links:

    Our simple web page may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of those third-party websites. We recommend reviewing the privacy policies of those websites before providing any personal information.

</p>
<p>
    6. Children's Privacy:

    Our simple web page is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will take steps to delete the information from our records.

</p>
<p>
    7. Changes to this Privacy Policy:

    We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. When we make changes, we will revise the "last updated" date at the beginning of the policy. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.

    By using our simple web page, you consent to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

    If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the use of your personal information, please contact us at [your contact email].
</p>
